cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.CV

The paper discusses the use of deep learning in computer security, specifically in malware detection and vulnerability discovery. This suggests that the paper could belong to the categories of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV). However, since the focus is on explaining the decision process of deep neural networks, cs.CR and cs.LG are the most likely categories.
